## Development

This repo includes a standard `Makefile`.

```bash
# one-time setup
make requirements

# run tests
make test

# install locally (editable)
make dev-install

# build & publish
make build
make publish-test
make publish
```

Alternatively, you can use the scripts under `scripts/` directly.

